atriots.win/post/cII4D6lRIVLZ.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/AgF39iQRkiPIEZBF.jpeg", "width": 680, "content-type": "jpeg", "height": 676}], "blurhash": "UZN0J0D*%$?G.TxtMxNH?^s.n$Rk?cs:s:az", "full_resolution": [676, 680]}, "title": "HAPPY 250TH BIRTHDAY PATRIOTS!", "last_comment_created": 1783230607976, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": true, "comments": 9, "score_up": 141, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ATBlwIpzk", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 80, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "truth", "id": 8713880, "raw_content": "", "author": "ohpleaseuhhelpame", "created": 1783213817310, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "truthsocial.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ATBlwIpzk.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://truthsocial.com/@realDonaldTrump/posts/116864681605523102", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": " I will be there no matter what, but the \u201cwhat\u201d usually turns out to be a good thing. It\u2019s Saturday night, LETS HAVE SOME FUN, even if we are out late tonight. They say 11:00 O\u2019Clock for the speech. Who cares??? ", "last_comment_created": 1783213817310, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 0, "score_up": 80, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"description": "Storms bring luck to whatever the occasion. They also make events a little bit more exciting! We will wait it out, I don\u2019t care if it\u2019s 2:00 O\u2019Clock in the morning, or in one hour from now. Looks like it is going to pass, they always do. I will be there no matter what, but the \u201cwhat\u201d usually turns out to be a good thing. It\u2019s Saturday night, LETS HAVE SOME FUN, even if we are out late tonight. They say 11:00 O\u2019Clock for the speech. Who cares??? Remember two weeks ago when the big UFC Event was at 100% chance of heavy rain, all week long, and just minutes before the card started. Well, there wasn\u2019t a single drop, and the fights turned out to be among the greatest in history, an event for the ages. Our great veterans, especially the old timers, many of whom are there, went through hellfire, and it didn\u2019t stop them. It\u2019s not going to stop us either! I\u2019m not going to let some rain stop our 250th. I\u2019m leaving the White House soon. God Bless America! President DONALD J. TRUMP", "large_image": "B7eElZdouw8oZj71.png", "title": "Donald J. Trump (@realDonaldTrump)"}, "post_flair_text": "\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0TRUMP\u00a0\u00a0TRUTH\u00a0\u00a0", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ATBlxP23e", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 53, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8714072, "raw_content": "", "author": "redditadminssuckit", "created": 1783222362495, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "2FBIAgents1Cup", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "media.scored.co", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ATBlxP23e.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://media.scored.co/post/YDWcEmIzeG2e.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/f9Jtwsy2fO4igtoc.jpeg", "width": 742, "content-type": "jpeg", "height": 768}], "blurhash": "U1Ss1@00,,~q9E9Fxu%N00-:_3%M4pM{a{WT", "full_resolution": [1485, 1434]}, "title": "Did you know that 31,000 WWII vets are still living?  Their numbers are dwindling at an exponential rate... the youngest are in their late 90's", "last_comment_created": 1783233243009, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": true, "comments": 5, "score_up": 53, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ATBlwI0Jk", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 196, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8713508, "raw_content": "", "author": "InfidelBaconEater", "created": 1783196379291, "profile_picture": "iw4PGYHDp1UM", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "media.scored.co", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ATBlwI0Jk.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://media.scored.co/post/bvQ1QljbXnnf.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/UPuwx0wYs5c2h6Lw.jpeg", "width": 568, "content-type": "jpeg", "height": 757}], "blurhash": "UOKKvQ9aM{M{~qkDRjj]ITa~ozR*t6j]WCof", "full_resolution": [757, 568]}, "title": "Talk about having skin in the game...\nMay God Bless these men and their families for eternity \ud83d\ude4f\ud83d\ude4f\ud83d\ude4f", "last_comment_created": 1783196379288, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": true, "comments": 0, "score_up": 196, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ATBlxPIm5", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 43, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8714125, "raw_content": "They do not respect our flag, our history, our people and our country! President Trump has to kick all these fucking assholes out of America. \n\nEvery GOP congress member who cried about SCOTUS ruling on birthright citizenship better vote to change the definition of the \"subject\" to the jurisdiction to mean only US citizens and LPR. The test for subject to the jurisdiction must be the mother's allegiance to which country, and only US citizens and LPR swore allegiance to the Flag of the United States of America, and to the Republic for which it stands, one Nation under God, indivisible, with liberty and justice for all.", "author": "Tomis_4", "created": 1783226023397, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Secession2030", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "America became the most powerful country in the world because we took care of our own. We are proud to be Americans and respect our heritage. Immigrants used to desperately want to be Americans and sacrificed everything to be here. Now, we have too many fucking losers in the country.", "last_comment_created": 1783230932673, "content": "<p>They do not respect our flag, our history, our people and our country! President Trump has to kick all these fucking assholes out of America.</p>\n<p>Every GOP congress member who cried about SCOTUS ruling on birthright citizenship better vote to change the definition of the &quot;subject&quot; to the jurisdiction to mean only US citizens and LPR. The test for subject to the jurisdiction must be the mother's allegiance to which country, and only US citizens and LPR swore allegiance to the Flag of the United States of America, and to the Republic for which it stands, one Nation under God, indivisible, with liberty and justice for all.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 2, "score_up": 43, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2073075120701354047", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ATBlvAR0j", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 750, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8712819, "raw_content": "", "author": "catsfive", "created": 1783170070842, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "midgetpornrocks", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/AlaskanRants/status/2073075120701354047", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "HAVE YOU SAID ''MURICA,' TODAY? Alaska's Glacier View car launch has run every year since 2005, when it started with a moose-killed rig that needed disposal, and tomorrow's 250th-birthday edition brings a Coast Guard flyover and bigger crowds to watch vehicles tumble 300 feet off a cliff.", "last_comment_created": 1783224625158, "content": "